@jonkime Hi Jon,

I appreciate where you are coming from but we are unable to provide any monetary refunds for cancelled flights. The voucher can be redeemed up to the value stated on the voucher in one booking within 6 months of issue, for travel within 12 months of the booking date.
@kingtiffreamie Hi there, Please DM us with your booking reference and full name so that we can see how we can assist you. Thanks-Jo
